title: The Football League Show 22.11.2014
description:
The Football League Show 22.11.2014 

Duration: 1 hour 20 min

The featured match this week sees two clubs with realistic promotion ambitions, Wolves and Nottingham Forest, go head-to-head at Molineux.
Plus highlights of the action from a west London derby as Brentford entertain Fulham, and Huddersfield meet Sheffield Wednesday.
Drama from all three divisions of the Football League brought to you by Manish Bhasin.
